04/05/2010
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- A huge explosion caused panic in Skopje early Tuesday (May 4th). 
Media initially reported that the blast could have been caused by a small aircraft or a drone. 
Authorities later described it as an explosion at a steel factory amid scrap metal. 
At least one worker was injured. 
(MIA, Makfax, A1, Sitel - 04/05/10)
